.TH ALARM 1
.SH NAME
alarm \- ask for delayed note
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B alarm
.I time
.I command 
[
.I arg ...
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Alarm
causes an
.B alarm
note (see
.IR notify (2))
to be sent to the process indicated by
.I command
after 
.I time
seconds.
.SH SOURCE
.B /sys/src/cmd/alarm.c
.SH SEE ALSO
.IR sleep (2)
